Dialga (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0482: Azelf
Pokémon
#0484: Palkia →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Dialga (TCG Pocket).

Dialga has been featured on 27 different cards since it debuted in the Diamond & Pearl expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Dialga cards are normally Metal-type or Dragon-type Basic Pokémon. As a Dragon-type, their attacks normally have costs including and Energy.
